devs = self.meross_manager.find_devices(device_class=ToggleXMixin,
    online_status=OnlineStatus.ONLINE)
if len(devs) < 1:
    self.skipTest('No available/online devices found to test. Skipping...')
dev = devs[0]
async def send_invalid_command_to_device(dev: BaseDevice):
    res = await self.meross_manager.async_execute_cmd(destination_device_uuid
        =dev.uuid, method='GET', namespace=Namespace.HUB_MTS100_MODE,
        payload={})
    return res
with self.assertRaises(CommandTimeoutError):
    await send_invalid_command_to_device(dev=dev)
unittest_run_loop
